headline: Is It Too Late To Consider KLA (KLAC) After Its Strong Multi Year Share Price Run
summary: If you are wondering whether KLA's share price still offers value after a strong run, this article will walk through what the numbers say and how to think about the current price tag. With the stock at US$1,324.60 and returns of 9.0% over 7 days, 8.1% over 30 days, 3.9% year to date and 94.7% over 1 year, KLA has clearly been on many investors' radar. headline: KLA Corporation (KLAC) Shares Skyrocket, What You Need To Know
summary: Shares of semiconductor manufacturing equipment maker KLA Corporation (NASDAQ:KLAC) jumped 5.1% in the morning session after Cantor Fitzgerald raised its price target on the stock to $1,750 from $1,500.
